      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Calling all mechanics and restoration fans! This car is the perfect project for someone looking to roll up their sleeves and bring a vehicle back to life. While it currently requires significant mechanical work and has visible wear and tear, it offers a fantastic foundation for a rebuild or a wealth of valuable parts. Grab this diamond in the rough at an unbeatable price and start your next automotive adventure today!",
